balization <br/>Pre-Requisite(s) Mental Clarity <br/>Level Requirement: 59 <br/>Ability Type: Activated&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/>Re-Use Time: 3 minutes <br/>Max Training: 1 Levels <br/>Point Cost: 5 <br/>Description: This ability takes a massive amount of life from the Shaman and replenshishes their mana. <br/>It takes 1924 hitpoints from the Shaman to give them 1200 mana back.<br/><br/>It can be re-used every 69 seconds, but must be used in relatively safe circumstances.<br/> <br/></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Shaman of the T<br/>Wolves of the Tundra<br/>Saryrn</td></tr>
